      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLACK WANDA (8) had to overcome a check in the run but could manage only a distant third (20.48) in a TG1-4W over 342m at this track. Has good speed and can quickly clear the pack out wide. Given another chance. KIM GOT GAME (4) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when second (20.18) at this track in a TG1-4W. Can improve sharply here. TAZ MANIAC (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (20.71) at this track behind Sebon Star in a TG1-4W. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Expected to feature again. SWIFT ASCENT (2) can measure up with the right run.",
